<div class="wysiwyg parbase section">
<div class="rte">
<p><b>MacMail</b></p>
<p>- From the&nbsp;main&nbsp;menu, select<i>&nbsp;Mail/Preferences<br>
</i>- Select the <i>Accounts</i> tab<br>
- If <i>Automatically Manage Connection Settings </i>is selected, you may already have the right configuration. Unselect <i>AMCS</i> and make sure <i>TLS/SSL</i> is selected. The port should be<i> 993.</i></p>

</div></div>


