<p>For security reasons, Concordia discourages the use of non-native mobile mail (Example: Microsoft Outlook for iOS and Android) apps to access the University"s mail service. To configure your device using the native mail applications, consult the <a adhocenable="false" href="http://www.concordia.ca/it/services/faculty-staff-email.html#mobile-devices">ActiveSync configuration instructions</a> on this page.</p>

