        </div>
        <div class="details">
            <label for="details"><b>This form is for feedback only.</b> Technical support requests should be submitted by email to <a href="mailto:help@concordia.ca">help@concordia.ca</a> </b> or phone 514-848-2424, ext. <b> 7613. </b> <p> </p> <p> Page suggestions:</label></br>
            <textarea id="details" name="details" rows=3 data-rule-required="true"></textarea>
        </div>
